  - elementId: table-caption
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 380, 1120, 24]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      text: |
        <p><strong>Table 2.</strong> 消融实验结果。分类任务报告ROC-AUC（↑），回归任务报告RMSE（↓）。<strong>加粗</strong>为最优。</p>

  # 分隔线
  - elementId: mid-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [80, 420, 1120, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#CFD8DC"

  # 分析文字
  - elementId: analysis-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 440, 300, 26]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>消融分析</strong></p>

  - elementId: analysis-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 473, 1120, 174]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      lineHeight: 1.7
      text: |
        <p><strong>注意力读出层</strong>贡献最为显著（平均+2.1%），尤其在HIV数据集上提升2.3%，表明不同原子对分子性质的贡献差异较大，自适应加权优于等权求和。</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><strong>边特征融合</strong>是第二大贡献因子（平均+3.2%），说明化学键类型和原子间距离信息对性质预测至关重要。</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><strong>MPNN层数</strong>从1层增至3层带来5.0%的平均提升，但进一步增至5层（未列出）提升不显著（+0.3%），存在过平滑风险。</p>

  # 底部线
  - elementId: bottom-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 716, 1280, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 4
      color: "$primary"

  # 页码
  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1150, 680, 80, 24]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "06 / 09"
